  "detailed_description": "<h1>ENDO Discord Server</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1507620/extras/690034f8f825cb256573c0c723cd5a5e.avif?t=1729438227\" width=610 height=64 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>discord . gg / yYhGzY2dZF</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >(Steam doesn't allow links anymore so I had to separate it with spaces)</p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><i>\"Like a fidget toy on mushrooms\"</i><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Every interaction in ENDO is physical.</h2>  <strong>By clicking and dragging in the first-person perspective, it behaves like a pseudo-VR experience.  Even the menus are physical and interactive.</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1507620/extras/489b2e6faa5ac4795057e54cbeb7e2e4.poster.avif?t=1729438227\" width=614 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1507620/extras/489b2e6faa5ac4795057e54cbeb7e2e4.webm?t=1729438227\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1507620/extras/489b2e6faa5ac4795057e54cbeb7e2e4.mp4?t=1729438227\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\">    <li><strong>Highly Tactile: </strong>There are lots of fun little objects to play around with - the world is like a musical fidget toy, filled with unexpected novelties.<br>    </li><li><strong>Immerse yourself in colorful and unique worlds: </strong>Each realm is brought to life with all sorts of bizarre creatures, plants and mushrooms.</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >My goal with ENDO is to create a dreamy, playful world for you to enjoy.</h2>  From the diversity of plants, to the miniature worlds of moss, fungi and lichen, I find that nature is a great inspiration. I wanted to emulate this sense of wonder with ENDO.<br><br><br><i>Peace and much love,<br>~Dez</i>",
  "about_the_game": "<i>\"Like a fidget toy on mushrooms\"</i><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Every interaction in ENDO is physical.</h2>  <strong>By clicking and dragging in the first-person perspective, it behaves like a pseudo-VR experience.  Even the menus are physical and interactive.</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1507620/extras/489b2e6faa5ac4795057e54cbeb7e2e4.poster.avif?t=1729438227\" width=614 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1507620/extras/489b2e6faa5ac4795057e54cbeb7e2e4.webm?t=1729438227\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1507620/extras/489b2e6faa5ac4795057e54cbeb7e2e4.mp4?t=1729438227\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\">    <li><strong>Highly Tactile: </strong>There are lots of fun little objects to play around with - the world is like a musical fidget toy, filled with unexpected novelties.<br>    </li><li><strong>Immerse yourself in colorful and unique worlds: </strong>Each realm is brought to life with all sorts of bizarre creatures, plants and mushrooms.</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >My goal with ENDO is to create a dreamy, playful world for you to enjoy.</h2>  From the diversity of plants, to the miniature worlds of moss, fungi and lichen, I find that nature is a great inspiration. I wanted to emulate this sense of wonder with ENDO.<br><br><br><i>Peace and much love,<br>~Dez</i>",
